              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Enriched 126Te (98.69% and 99.8%) by electroplating on",
                " Ti foils. The deposit was covered by Al foil (10 um",
                " thick)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Covered proton energy range: 5-100 MeV,",
                "beam current: 100 nA (low to avoid loss of iodine",
                "during the irradiation).",
                "The targets were irradiated together with beam",
                "monitors.",
                "Nondestructive measurement.",
                "All measurements were done repeatedly to follow the",
                "decay of the nuclides, and the contributions of",
                "different nuclides to the same gamma-ray were",
                "separated."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " High-resolution detectors.",
                "The low energy gamma-ray (35.5 keV) of 125I demanded a",
                "suitably calibrated low-energy detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In general, the total uncertainty amounted to between",
                "9 and 23%. In the case of 126Te(p,2n)125I reaction",
                "the errors are about 45%."
